overview: 2016 recording of the show by Dutch comedian Paulien Cornelisse. In this performance Cornelisse is concerned with all things that seem and may be unimportant, the unnoticed things. She takes a close look at them and subjects them to a thorough analysis. Social issues such as the treatment of a right-cylindrical garbage can are discussed, but there is also an eye for the emotional life of a yellow parakeet.
title: Paulien Cornelisse: Maar Ondertussen
